AndreaMosaic is a other tool allows you to transform photos into mosaics created from collection of photos of you. The manner of operation of the program is very simple, but it does not always give you the results you are looking for. The user must choose the image collection you want to use to create the mosaic and the photo will be converted on AndreaMosaic.
&nbsp;
AndreaMosaic allows you to configure a number of options, such as width the last of the mosaic, the number of images on...
